longBusinessSummary: PC Jeweller Limited manufactures, retails, and trades in gold, diamond and diamond studded jewelry, silver, and gemstone jewelry in India. It offers rings, earrings, pendants, gold chains, bracelets and bangles, nose pins, necklaces, and mangalsutra, as well as men's jewelry. The company sells its jewelry through its showrooms, franchisee showrooms, and Website. The company also exports its products. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Delhi, India.
